Privacy Policy
This is World of Secrets's Privacy Policy.
Overview
We care about protecting your privacy. Your privacy is taken very seriously and therefore we aim to comply with all privacy regulations worldwide especially with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA). This Privacy Policy describes the information collected by World of Secrets through mobile applications and how we use that information.
Our apps are developed for iOS and Android. We publish them on App Store and Google Play. Apps and data collected differ from one platform to another. Therefore this privacy policy is described in two parts - one for iOS and App Store and the other for Android and Google Play.
iOS - App Store
Our apps published on App Store are free, contain no ads and do not use any third-party analytics. Therefore we do not collect any user information from apps on iOS.
Android - Google Play
Apps we publish on Google Play are free and contain ads.
We don’t collect any personal information. But some Non-personally identifiable information may be gathered while you use our apps. Non-personally identifiable information is general, non-identifiable and anonymous information that is gathered for analytical purposes such as the improvement of our apps.
To achieve the best experience in our apps, we work with third party service providers. We also work with ad networks AdMob (Google) and Unity Ads (Unity) to serve ads in our apps. These networks are restricted from tracking users and serving behavioral ads.
Additionally, these networks are part of the Google Play certified ad network program. For more information about this program please visit the Google Play website:
https://play.google.com/about/monetization-ads/ad-network/
These ad networks also participate in the Family Ads program, which validates ads safe for kids.
https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/9283445?hl=en
Our third party partners, and their privacy policies are as follows:
