Our apps are built with Unity and use the Unity In-App Purchases service which requires Unity Analytics to run. Unity Analytics does not share user data.
Unity Analytics Privacy Policy:
https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
We use Firebase analytics to track installs, in-app purchases and the number of ads watched. Firebase does not collect any personal information in order to provide us with this information.
Firebase Privacy Policy:
https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy
